item.description: Introduction Bored of your stock performance here are some hacks to revitalize your ride performance and to enhance the drivability. When it comes to additional torque, People are ready to spend thousands of bucks to an EFI tuner and other kind of performance garages. But with the lack of knowledge on these actual stuffs may lead to ruin your car or end up with some expensive lessons. So it is important to know what is actually done in a performance garage to proliferate those additional horses.
